<!-- -*- markdown -*- -->

About
====================
This is a video addon for sc2casts.com for xbmc.

Features
====================
* Browsing of Lastest/Most viewed
* Playback of vods

Installing
====================
* Download [plugin.video.gomtv.net-0.0.3.zip](https://bitbucket.org/henrik/plugin.video.gomtv.net/downloads/plugin.video.gomtv.net-0.0.3.zip)
* Start xbmc and navigate to system -> add-ons -> install from zip file, browse to the file.
* You're done! Use the add-on from the add-ons item in the video-browser.

